**Systems:** `[ "x86_64-linux" "aarch64-linux" "aarch64-darwin" "x86_64-darwin" ]`

**Platform-native deps:** `lib.optionals pkgs.stdenv.isLinux [...]` and `lib.optionals pkgs.stdenv.isDarwin [...]` for system libs. Use `config.home.homeDirectory` for paths.

**Conditional config:** `lib.mkMerge` + `lib.mkIf` for enable flags and platform splits.

**Canonical:** @Desktop/shells/default.nix, @Desktop/home-manager/programs/git.nix, @Desktop/home-manager/programs/ssh.nix, @Desktop/home-manager/modules/zsh.nix, @Desktop/home-manager/modules/lf.nix
